# $Id$

Scripts for mail processing.

Available scripts:

  xmlrpcdeliver
    -> an XML-RPC delivery agent for postfix (/sendmail ??)

  DeliverToProject.py
    -> needs xmlrpcdeliver setup in postfix
    -> delivers Mails into a OpenGroupware.org project

  DeliverWeblogs.py
    -> needs xmlrpcdeliver setup in postfix
    -> delivers weblog Mails into filesystem
       destination path config in OGO project file '/logaliases.txt'

xmlrpcdeliver contains a full xmlrpclib !
---snip---
